text: Old school, nostalgic coffee shop. Only have 4 stores, drink, mix veg, chicken rice and indian store. Place is very spacious and hidden. Must go before this place is redevelop.

Just 4 food stalls and 1 drinks stall. Price is not really cheap considering the location and vicinity it served. A canteen that serves nearby companies. However, there is a deep pond with 4 very big fishes.
polite and smiling counter lady, taste doesn't matter lol~
Nice hideout in d hot sun 2 eat n rest
Nice Teo chew porridge. And there's Arapaima to see.
